---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Gophy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Gophy. Learn how we handle your data."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Gophy ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information
          when you use our Chrome extension and related services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">2.1 Audio Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          During active meetings, we process audio in real-time to provide suggestions.
          <strong>Audio is never stored.</strong> It is processed transiently and discarded
          immediately after generating suggestions.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">2.2 Account Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          When you create an account, we collect your email address and authentication
          credentials through Google Sign-In. We do not store passwords.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">2.3 Usage Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We collect anonymized usage metrics to improve our service, including meeting
          duration and feature usage. This data cannot be traced back to individual users.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>To provide real-time AI suggestions during your meetings</li>
          <li>To authenticate your account and manage your subscription</li>
          <li>To improve our AI models and service quality</li>
          <li>To communicate with you about your account and updates</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption in transit
          (TLS 1.3), secure authentication, and regular security audits. Audio data is
          processed in isolated, ephemeral environments.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Google Cloud</strong> - Authentication and infrastructure</li>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> - Payment processing</li>
          <li><strong>Deepgram</strong> - Speech-to-text processing (no audio retention)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          You have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your account and data</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:privacy@gophy.ai" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">
            privacy@gophy.ai
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
